Ba Jail Minecraftpiston
===========================

Map created by Exel80 

**Games:**

- Climb
- Deathrun
- Talent
- Gun toss
- Hole in the wall
- Volleyball
- Soccer
- Race
- Disco
- Basketball


Change Log
==========

#### **Version 6 FINAL _(3.1.2012)_**
- Fix texture bug
- Fix ladder bug
- Fix again climb and race "stop" button

#### **Version 5 FINAL _(1.1.2012)_**
- Added tree & long grass
- Fix race & climb stop button
- Fix hole in the wall
- Fix Disco door.
- Remove Wipeout

#### **Version 4 FINAL _(6.9.2011)_**
- Fix climb buttons.
- Added sound Talent and Soccer.
- Added the Stop button on the Race.
- Edit Deathrun.
- Remove one pistol in jail.

#### **Version 3 BETA _(3.9.2011)_**
- Fix some bugs.

#### **Version 2 BETA _(1.9.2011)_**
- Fix Disco room.
- Fix Gun Toss sign, Disco sign and Hole in the wall sign.

#### **Version 1 BETA _(1.9.2011)_**
- Added in gamebanana.
- Fix some bugs.
